<para>Only rules that have a confirmed 1:1 mapping to a C# <computeroutput>DispatchingRule</computeroutput> are included. The inline comments document the corresponding C# enum value for each rule. Rules without a C# equivalent (e.g. <computeroutput>most_operations_remaining</computeroutput>) can be included here for reference but will produce unmatched rows in the comparison. </para>
